<p>Below are examples of embedding the form widgets.</p>
<p>The snippets include `script` tags for automatically resizing the iframes. These are optional but recormended for the best experience. For more options for the `iframeResize` function see the <a href="https://github.com/davidjbradshaw/iframe-resizer">documentation here</a></p>
<p>If the parent page contains Google Analytics tags, then the tracking-id and client-id will be passed through to the iframe and `support` events will be triggered with actions of `register` and `signup` tied to the client-id</p>

